<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>For Issay ❤️</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4);
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }.container {
  padding: 60px 20px;
}

h1 {
  font-size: 3em;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

h2 {
  font-weight: normal;
  margin-top: 0;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

p {
  font-size: 1.2em;
  max-width: 650px;
  margin: 20px auto;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.heart {
  font-size: 3em;
  animation: heartbeat 1s infinite;
  margin: 20px 0;
}

@keyframes heartbeat {
  0% { transform: scale(1); }
  25% { transform: scale(1.2); }
  50% { transform: scale(1); }
  75% { transform: scale(1.2); }
  100% { transform: scale(1); }
}

.btn {
  background: #fff;
  color: #ff6f91;
  border: none;
  padding: 15px 25px;
  font-size: 1em;
  border-radius: 25px;
  cursor: pointer;
  margin: 10px;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

.btn:hover {
  background: #ffe0e9;
}

.hidden-message {
  display: none;
  margin-top: 25px;
  font-size: 1.3em;
  animation: fadeIn 1s ease forwards;
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

footer {
  margin-top: 40px;
  font-size: 0.9em;
  opacity: 0.8;
}

audio {
  display: none;
}

  </style>
</head>
<body>  <!-- Background Music -->  <audio autoplay loop>
    <!-- Replace the src below with a valid MP3 file of the song -->
    <source src="maikees-letter.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
  </audio>  <div class="container">
    <h1>Hi Issay 💖</h1>
    <h2>From Merill</h2><p>
  Every moment with you feels like something out of a dream. You make my world softer,
  brighter, and a whole lot more meaningful. If I had to choose again, it would always be you.
</p>

<div class="heart">❤️</div>

<h2>Do you love me?</h2>

<button class="btn" onclick="showMessage()">Yes 💘</button>
<button class="btn" onclick="showMessage()">Yes (obviously) 💞</button>

<p class="hidden-message" id="secret">
  I knew it. I love you more than anything, Issay. Always and forever. 💖
</p>

<footer>
  Made with love by Merill 💌
</footer>

  </div>  <script>
    function showMessage() {
      document.getElementById('secret').style.display = 'block';
    }
  </script></body>
</html>
